thread.title: Maria Schmidt

author: Maria Schmidt
title: Maria Schmidt
text:
As i placed the first order and received the products and the goodies i was testing them with the best result so far (good quality and a good results on the skin). Therefore i cant complain even if the high customs payment that i had to bear for the first shipment. There is a great product availability and a good translation.
Thanks for these amazing products :))
